{"tid":693220,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[overlord]你認為NPC的戰鬥排名","createTime":"2018-06-07T09:53:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T04:13:40.000Z","uid":53538,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7ea634fac188eec1abf0c0d46967c3ed3ec48ab8","tid":693220,"uid":53538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T09:53:12.000Z","msg":"目前overlord講咗係第三季出現後 引起唔少overlord迷討論人物既戰力.<br />\n所以我想係呢個post引起各位討論 首先想討論 1v1 and 多p<br />\n首先係講規則: 要係已知npc職業/大部分技能(盧貝多等少出現既唔可以參加),只限大墳墓NPC<br />\n1V1<br />\n唔可以召喚/叫人,唔可以食血水(技能除外),平地戰(可以技能改變),無限時間<br />\n多p<br />\n只可以召喚但唔可以叫人,唔可以食血水(技能除外),平地戰(可以技能改變),無限時間<br />\n<br />\n個人認為<br />\n1v1<br />\n塞巴斯&gt;潘朵拉&gt;夏提雅&gt;雅兒貝德=科塞特斯&gt;馬雷&gt;亞烏菈&gt;小迪<br />\n多p<br />\n馬雷=亞烏菈&gt;科塞特斯&gt;夏提雅&gt;雅兒貝德&gt;塞巴斯&gt;潘朵拉&gt;小迪<br />\n<br />\n不服來辯<br />\n<br />\n利伸:個人ff"},{"pid":"e1793e7e59d43fe5d9d453b7f8447b0f567ad6f7","tid":693220,"uid":34293,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T10:02:42.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"367d8ae29689e09afbffc5c4bee33f4e49973579","tid":693220,"uid":16123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T10:08:42.000Z","msg":"唔太熟<br />\n1v1好難講<br />\n個人感覺夏提雅好似勁D, 職業能力配搭<br />\n塞巴斯拳闘肉博好似最勁<br />\n科塞特斯就用近戰武器最勁<br />\n雅兒貝德好似係防守好強"},{"pid":"423bbda6994387d47304f16de033d08e3fb9a8f9","tid":693220,"uid":187600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T10:09:21.000Z","msg":"覺得潘朵拉1v1打唔過夏提雅"},{"pid":"8691591279996cdf4ed14fafe08533384fb2a70f","tid":693220,"uid":8307,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T10:09:51.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"720597085378292026fcd9258cba3a7cdba5d63d","tid":693220,"uid":35667,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T10:10:46.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"d4801301d5ba34fcb1a4ea61975b214509353631","tid":693220,"uid":33651,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T10:12:36.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"a2b331ac91aed830bf39d5930f62cfcc57180158